ike":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T12:34:47.000Z","msg":"翼翼我想食呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n亂炒一通無所謂，好食就得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4cd318d50280a5481b0117630f94f406ed2f444a","tid":318483,"uid":29329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T12:41:23.000Z","msg":"炒完相都冇張 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a87e57daacfaec442d51d66bbd6ba8de67b6d520","tid":318483,"uid":73160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T12:47:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>蛋都無打<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n一野轟落去炒埋一碟咪得<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有時飲macchiato同炒蛋一樣<br />\nMix咗就無咁多層次<br />\n開頭有奶味, 慢慢有咖啡味，飲最頂有espresso嘅濃厚<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你炒碟飯都咁屈機"},{"pid":"0f0a7e8321e8bf18a15e0ef83ca60a25dc5e9b76","tid":318483,"uid":29684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T12:47:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>翼翼我想食呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n亂炒一通無所謂，好食就得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好感動啊吉妹<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我炒比你食啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9c2bb4d3e3385d8e0193682063098a8f24815b3","tid":318483,"uid":71166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T12:52:10.000Z","msg":"腸腸 飯飯 蛋蛋 都好好味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"